	* : libavogadro/src/engines/labelengine.cpp; push all GL attribute
	  bits and use
	  white text.

	  libavogadro/src/tools/clickmeasure.cpp; push all GL attributes,
	  give feedback
	  on initial click (marked with *0) for now.

